Hi all,

I cannot for the life of me find the Zoom link for the 10:00AM call Thurs AM. I am not seeing it on the Agenda list on the Whova app. Can anyone help me out?

Mike
Hi @Michael Cox , it looks like the 10AM stream is coming up through Whova. If you go to Agenda->Thursday->9AM->45 Subsessions->CARIN Consumer Directed Payer Data Exchange it shoudl get you there
